dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Hsia-Mien. In upper left margin: China city plans 1:12,500. Polyconic projection. Relief shown by 20 meter with auxiliary 10 meter contours and spot elevations. Depth shown by fathoms. Pinyin name for this city: Xiamen. Chinese place names transcribed according to the modified Wade-Giles system. With Chinese-English glossary.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1946.
